    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a recently serviced dual-VANOS system. This example utilizes the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, sending power to a limited-slip rear differential. The chassis has undergone proactive subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. Suspension components remain tight, featuring a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear configuration. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with spirited use, the powertrain is dialed in, providing the linear power delivery and visceral induction note these naturally aspirated icons are known for.",
