      "description": "This vehicle has been exceptionally well-cared for and presents beautifully. The exterior maintains a high-gloss finish, with only minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, shallow scratch near the rear wheel well consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is immaculate and smoke-free; the premium upholstery shows light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster but remains free of tears or stains. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the infotainment system, operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is robust. I have adhered strictly to the factory service schedule, including a recent full synthetic oil change and a cooling system flush. The tires offer plenty of life with deep tread remaining, and the brake pads were replaced within the last 5,000 miles. It drives straight, shifts smoothly, and offers a quiet, composed ride. This is a dependable, turnkey vehicle for a buyer who appreciates a car that has been treated with respect.",
      "price": 34500.0,
