    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. She\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a weekend road trip, this car is super reliable and ready for its next adventure! It\u2019s got a few tiny signs of character here and there, but honestly, it still looks and runs great. Come take it for a spin\u2014I think you\u2019ll love it as much as I have!",
